This note shows my troubleshooting procedure for no alert showing in my Wazuh Instance. I have run the following
# Check status of filebeat
systemctl status filebeat
# Check filebeat can actually reach the indexer with its stored credentials
~#sudo filebeat test output -c /etc/filebeat/filebeat.yml
# Since i saw that there is Error 401 Unauthorized, this means there is credential mismatch.
sudo filebeat keystore add username --force
# type: admin
sudo filebeat keystore add password --force
# type: youradminpassword
# Restart Filebeat
sudo systemctl restart filebeat
sleep 10
sudo filebeat test output -c /etc/filebeat/filebeat.yml
# Expected output: talk to server... OK
